OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalian PM Mario Draghi    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fresigns after week of      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fturmoil                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A year-and-a-half after he was         
OL,6, appointed as Italy's unelected head of 
OL,7, a unity government, Mario Draghi has   
OL,8, resigned as prime minister.            
OL,10,FHe told President Sergio Mattarella he 
OL,11,Fwas standing down after three parties  
OL,12,Fin his government refused to back him  
OL,13,Fin a confidence vote the night before. 
OL,15,FThe president asked him to remain as   
OL,16,Fcaretaker leader and early elections   
OL,17,Fare expected this autumn.              
OL,19,FMr Draghi, 74, is a popular figure in  
OL,20,FItaly.                                 
